t\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">5- STAGE SWITCH TACTICAL FLASHLIGHT: This multi-mode LED tactical flashlight comes with five stages including low, mid, high, SOS and lastly strobe; easily switch between the five modes by engaging the pressure push on/off button at the back of the flashlight</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ADJUSTABLE FOCUS HEAD: By simply pushing and pulling the flashlight body in and out, the beam of LED light will be easily adjustable depending on the intended or needed use; zoom in or out between x1, x250, x500, x1000 or x2000; the flashlight also features a texturized grip for easy handling and comfort</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">GLOW IN THE DARK ON/OFF BUTTON: The ASR Tactical Black Compact Multi Mode 500 Lumen LED flashlight comes with a convenient pressure push on/off button that glows in the dark, allowing you to easily and quickly access the power end of the flashlight</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">HANDY WRIST STRAP: Featuring a useful and handy wrist strap, secure the compact, LED tactical flashlight around your wrist when in use; when not employed, use the strap to attach to a backpack, inner pocket, work bag and more via carabiner or clip making it easy to locate and store</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Length: 5.25 inches; Color: Black; Watt: 10W; Lumen: 500; Batteries: x3 AAA required (not included)</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Tactical 5.25 Inch Compact Multi Mode 500 Lumen LED Flashlight Wrist Strap</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">29.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>ASR Tactical Multi Mode 500 Lumen LED Flashlight may only measure 5.25 inches but, it comes with great and practical built-in features that will make it your go to flashlight—read on!\n\n-5-Stage Switch: easily maneuver between SOS, Strobe, Low, Medium and High light\n-Adjustable focus head (zoom in or out between x1, x250, x500, x1000 or x2000)\n-500 Lumen brightness\n-10W LED bulb\n-Glow in the dark on/off button\n-Convenient wrist strap\n-Patrial texturized handle \n\nCompact, lightweight and easy to handle, this ASR Outdoor multi-mode flashlight is meant to perform for any at home, field or tactical work needs and tasks. The flashlight as mentioned above, comes with a handy wrist strap that allows you to secure the tactical tool to your wrist when employed; the wrist strap also makes it easy to attach to an inner pocket, backpack or work bag via a clip or carabiner for storage or travel when not in use. \n\nLength: 5.25 inches\n\nBatteries: x3 AAA (not included)</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t<table>&nbsp;</table>\n\t</div>\n</body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pa